              <h1>
                
  When NBT Is Used More Than Fiat (Or Nu and Market Manipulation)

              </h1>
            </div>
          </header>
          <section class="row page_content">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                
<div class="row container">
  
  <div class="col-md-4 sidebar">

    <div class="scroll_title">
      <p class="supertitle">Article  <span style="breadcrumb-separator">//</span> Nu <span style="breadcrumb-separator">/</span> NuBits</p>
      <p class="title">When NBT is used more than fiat (or Nu and Market Manipulation)</p>
      <p class="author">By 
        nagalim
        
      </p>
      <p class="meta_text date">
